    /*       STORAGE-BASED RANGE LAZY SHUFFLING OPERATIONS        */
    /*.•°:°.´+˚.*°.˚:*.´•*.+°.•°:´*.´•*.•°.•°:°.´:•˚°.*°.˚:*.´+°.•*/

